column4: Q1 Q1: First I would like to ask you about your current situation / family situation. How would you rate it on a scale from 1 to 5?

Q10 Q10: On a scale ranging from 1 to 5 in which “1” means “not prepared at all” and “5” means “very prepared”, how do evaluate how you feel in terms of how school/university/work/vocational training prepares you for a good future life?
